text: The rumors are true: the cafeteria at Google is very good.
They also have Pour Over coffee with Google/Stumptown branded beans

attachments.title: Dumpling Week - Oregonian Media Group
attachments.text: The Oregonian and OregonLive present the second annual Dumpling Week, seven days of stories and deliciousness dedicated to our favorite dish. With features, recipes and promotions in The Oregonian's FoodDay and A&E sections, we'll be encouraging readers in print and online to go out and make dumpling week their own. Be sure to come
